Battera:;

She flew towards the signal.  The terrrane was changing. Instead of 
mountains, it was turning into a lush, green valley. She flew down 
and kept homing on CyerShark's signal. She couldn't wait to see him 
again.

She finally landed, about a half a mile from the signal. She 
transformed into bot mode and started walking. She opened up her 
link. "OK, I'm almost there. But where are you? How'd you get here."
